These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, coffee, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, cooking, singing, chess
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking milk##7
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | almond-milk       | lemonade | milk        |
| Hobby      | singing  | cooking | chess        | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, horse, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, golf, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the owner of the horse##7
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | horse | cat       | frog         | bird     |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | parkour | golf | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, drama, disaster, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, metal, ambient, electronic
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the fan of metal and the fan of folk##7
3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the person watching drama movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | martial-arts | disaster | family  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | folk  | electronic   | metal |

