.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, reading, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, parkour, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
3. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | dancing | sudoku       | reading |
| Sport   | cricket      | swimming   | parkour | skiing  |

