.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, dancing, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, polish, mexican, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the thai is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
5. the thai is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the polish is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | puzzles   | card-games | fishing |
| Nationality   | indonesian      | polish | thai      | mexican |

