.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, juice, fanta
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, colombian, pakistani, french
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the pakistani is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the french is somewhere between the italian and the colombian##7
7. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade | tea      | juice | fanta     |
| Nationality   | italian    | french | colombian   | pakistani |

