.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, kale, strawberry, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, dutch, russian
1. the mexican is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3
4. the russian is somewhere between the person eating potato and the person eating strawberry##7
5. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person eating strawberry##5
6. the russian is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | avocado    | potato   | kale | strawberry  |
| Nationality   | mexican | dutch | russian    | pakistani |

