.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, egyptian, indian
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, cat, hedgehog
1. the indonesian is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the indian is the owner of the cat##1
4. the egyptian is somewhere between the indian and the chinese##7
5. the indonesian is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | indonesian | chinese |
| Pet           | cat   | hedgehog    | fish       | turtle  |

