4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is between the person watching western movies and the fan of funk##2
6. the fan of house is somewhere between the fan of funk and the person watching western movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
