3. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person driving the helicopter##6
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
