The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, subway
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the owner of the frog##7
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | frog    | guinea-pig | mouse     | rat |
| Transport   | jet-ski | subway  | car | bike |

 